19:56.595 --> 19:58.330 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
AMY WALTER: I agree.

19:58.364 --> 20:01.667 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: On the Colin
Powell thing, he
has reportedly said: I told her
that I used

20:01.700 --> 20:02.701 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
my AOL account.

20:02.735 --> 20:04.437 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
That worked better.

20:04.470 --> 20:08.474 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He, by no means -- nobody is
