20:08.507 --> 20:12.178 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
So, you know, there is that.

20:12.211 --> 20:17.316 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Judicial Watch, which is a
conservative group
that has been looking for
problems for Hillary

20:17.349 --> 20:20.419 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Clinton, has been releasing a
