of e-mails.

20:20.453 --> 20:23.189 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And some of this is part of
that.

20:23.222 --> 20:28.761 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And there is this question that
keeps coming
up about the Clinton Foundation
and the relationship

20:28.794 --> 20:32.164 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
