that Secretary
Clinton did.

20:40.406 --> 20:42.508 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: But, Amy, the
bottom line is,
does this hurt her?

20:42.541 --> 20:43.509 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
AMY WALTER: Right.

20:43.542 --> 20:45.778 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It keeps coming back to, well,
two things.

20:45.811 --> 20:49.315 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If you're going to pin something
on somebody,
first, make sure they know that
you are going

20:49.348 --> 20:50.316 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to do that.

20:50.349 --> 20:51.317 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And, second, make sure they have
a buy-in.

20:51.350 --> 20:52.318 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Right?

20:52.351 --> 20:54.286 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You probably should do both
those things.

20:54.320 --> 21:00.226 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the second is, we just live
in a world
that's very different from the
way it was

21:00.259 --> 21:07.032 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
