town in the
country.

51:09.133 --> 51:10.734 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
This trailer can serve about 200
to 300 people?

51:10.768 --> 51:13.037 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DAVID BLAIS: Right, just about
200 to 300.

51:13.070 --> 51:15.906 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TINA MARTIN: And how many times
are you going
out a week?

51:15.940 --> 51:18.375 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DAVID BLAIS: We go out three
nights a week
with the trailer, and then we do
something

51:18.409 --> 51:20.844 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
