Freddie Franjul's
neighborhood, where seeing the
truck is a

51:26.617 --> 51:28.285 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
huge relief.

51:28.319 --> 51:30.821 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
FREDDIE FRANJUL, Father:
Actually, it's a
big deal for pretty much family
around here,

51:30.854 --> 51:32.756 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
